ercise&quot;:false,&quot;landing_page_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_asset_id&quot;:134367,&quot;preview_url&quot;:&quot;/course/24823/preview/?startPreviewId=134367&quot;,&quot;learn_url&quot;:&quot;/course/java-tutorial/learn/lecture/137076&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Multi-Dimensional Arrays&quot;,&quot;object_index&quot;:16,&quot;item_type&quot;:&quot;lecture&quot;},{&quot;can_be_previewed&quot;:false,&quot;content_summary&quot;:&quot;11:44&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;It\u0026#039;s finally time to take a look at classes and objects, the main building blocks of OO (Object Oriented) programming.&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:137826,&quot;icon_class&quot;:&quot;udi udi-play-circle&quot;,&quot;is_coding_exercise&quot;:false,&quot;landing_page_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_asset_id&quot;:134874,&quot;preview_url&quot;:&quot;/course/24823/preview/?startPreviewId=134874&quot;,&quot;learn_url&quot;:&quot;/course/java-tutorial/learn/lecture/137826&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Classes and Objects&quot;,&quot;object_index&quot;:17,&quot;item_type&quot;:&quot;lecture&quot;},{&quot;can_be_previewed&quot;:false,&quot;content_summary&quot;:&quot;11:05&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;\u003cp\u003e\n\tClasses (and objects) can contain data and subroutines, the latter being referred to as \u0026quot;methods\u0026quot;. We\u0026#039;ll look at methods here.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\n\tNote: there\u0026#039;s a little error right at the end here -- I copied person1.sayHello() but didn\u0026#039;t change it to person2 ..\n\u003c/p\u003e&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:138666,&quot;icon_class&quot;:&quot;udi udi-play-circle&quot;,&quot;is_coding_exercise&quot;:false,&quot;landing_page_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_asset_id&quot;:135583,&quot;preview_url&quot;:&quot;/course/24823/preview/?startPreviewId=135583&quot;,&quot;learn_url&quot;:&quot;/course/java-tutorial/learn/lecture/138666&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Methods&quot;,&quot;object_index&quot;:18,&quot;item_type&quot;:&quot;lecture&